Hello everyone
I have a question, how to convert corona 7 to 6 version. I get scene in corona 7 that i need to fix, but i have 6 version?
snippet.textOriginal:
Hello everyone
I have a question, how to convert corona 7 to 6 version. I get scene in corona 7 that i need to fix, but i have 6 version?

snippet.textDisplay: Hi! Sorry, it is not possible to convert from new to old versions. Best option is just to install Corona 7 (it's better all round!); as a note you can even have two versions of Corona installed at any one time, see https://coronarenderer.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/12000066819-how-to-run-different-versions-of-corona-renderer-at-the-same-time-corona-5-and-newer- hope this helps! Tom
